Package: DataPreparation
Title: General-Purpose Data Preparation and Feature Engineering Library
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("AARICHE", "ABDERRAHIM", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive, modular R package for data preparation and feature engineering.
    Provides functions for missing value handling, numeric feature transformations, 
    string/text analysis, n-gram generation, linguistic feature extraction, and advanced 
    pattern discovery. Functions are general-purpose and reusable across different projects 
    and datasets.
